text: Gorodetsky (masculine), Gorodetskaya (feminine), or Gorodetskoye (neuter) may refer to: *Gorodetsky (surname) *Gorodetsky District, a district of Nizhny Novgorod Oblast, Russia *Gorodetsky (rural locality) (Gorodetskaya, Gorodetskoye), name of several rural localities in Russia ==See also== *Mayak Gorodetsky, a rural locality in Ostrovnoy, Murmansk Oblast, Russia
title: Gorodetsky
